      <title>GoldenTree 将购买爱尔兰银行 8 亿欧元英国贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/goldentree-to-buy-800-million-of-uk-loans-from-bank-of-ireland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，GoldenTree Asset Management 同意从爱尔兰银行集团有限公司购买相当于约 8 亿欧元（8.72 亿美元）的英国消费贷款组合。]]></description>
